rows.label: tlk70000022_01_msg0001
rows.name:
This city has a long history. There's
shops been here more'n 300 years.

rows.label: tlk70000022_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I myself come from 14 generations
of craftsmen. We've been building
in Iira for a long time.

rows.label: tlk70000022_01_msg0003
rows.name:
It's a fair old task, taking on the weight
of that history while adapting to the
demands of the time.

rows.label: tlk70000022_01_msg0004
rows.name:
This city's built on blood, sweat
and tears. More than you know.
